---
title: Striploin Steak and Easy Scalloped Potatoes with Herby Mushrooms and Green Beans
description: Tender striploin steak and our creamy, dreamy scalloped potatoes are guaranteed to make dinner extra special We've simplified the potatoes by cutting them into rounds and pre-boiling in sauce – no mandolines and long baking times tonight!
